# Go CI Node Variant

This variant extends the base Go CI image with Node.js support for polyglot projects.

## Included Tools

- Go compiler
- Node.js {{ .Versions.nodejs }}
- Zig build tool

## Usage

```dockerfile
FROM __hive__/go-ci:1.26.0-node

# Build Go application
RUN go build -o myapp .

# Install Node dependencies
RUN npm install
```